{"tid":409579,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白人空姐整到變黑人巨胸女 「做黑人好啲」","createTime":"2017-09-22T07:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T14:45:41.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":119,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab5a945584198ffa44a05f3f5d91b329a7e262e","tid":409579,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170922/large/1506055580_b7f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170922%2Flarge%2F1506055580_b7f3.jpg&h=7d512661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n憑一對32S假胸自稱「歐洲第一巨乳」、並多次接受黑色素注射將白晢肌膚變黑的德國女模馬丁娜（Martina Big），近日又有出位言論。她登上美國電視清淡節目時堅稱自己是黑人，惹來網民狠轟。<br />\n<br />\n本是白人的馬丁娜多次接受黑色素注射，並曬自家強力太陽燈達致夢寐以求的黑膚色，她在節目《The Maury Show》稱：「我是黑人，這是我的種族，我聽說過非洲的食物很美味，很想飛去當地品嚐。當黑人比較好，自我感覺也較好。我對一身黑膚色感驕傲，縱使顏色會褪，我也不會少了當黑人的感覺，我會要他們（美容院）再添一點（顏色）。」<br />\n<br />\n她形容自己是「80%黑人」，因為有不少與黑人相關的東西或習慣要學習。當主持問到她有否認為自己的言行冒犯了黑人，她稱：「沒有，我不想這樣。我知道有人感冒犯但那並非我的本意。我是為了自己變成這樣（黑人），也是在有人問我時才談及這話題。」<br />\n<br />\n網民對她的奇言奇行大表反感，形容她是個白癡，「明顯是有問題的女人」等。馬丁娜7月時亦曾拍片自稱是黑人，有看過片段的黑人女子慨嘆：「這是悲哀的。這是可憐的。為何你改變膚色來看似某些人種？」馬丁娜當時回應：「我如今是個真正的黑人女人&hellip;&hellip;為何你就是不能接受？」<br />\n<br />\n她在2012年首次整容，當時她想變成加拿大巨胸女星彭美拉安德遜（Pamela Anderson）或英國巨胸女模佐敦（Katie Price，前稱Jordan），但之後覺得她們「線條美」不夠，決定大灑5萬鎊（約53萬港元）隆胸變成32S巨乳。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》/《蘋果》資料室  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170922/large/1506055601_818e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170922%2Flarge%2F1506055601_818e.jpg&h=3c351ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170922/large/1506055600_014b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170922%2Flarge%2F1506055600_014b.jpg&h=b791dc24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170922/57240637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170922%2F57240637&d=%2B5%2FyjJ4Eu%2Fq2kyZLlrbNTx4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=b70f0f12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170922%2F57240637&h=9951bd12\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170922/57240637</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TAwqvqc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTAwqvqc.gif&h=80fc0231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n增加難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9748387c551059344c0113ce7a9f18678e310362","tid":409579,"uid":148761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:40:53.000Z","msg":"就黎斷咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0893576a186df6a214f68328ee81fa2174c9168f","tid":409579,"uid":39,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"Get out ?"},{"pid":"2645052a9581bf1652810fc50654361c3e9629fa","tid":409579,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Get out ?</blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"a1c6b05fd7ded899792d94a2741ef811891ef1f1","tid":409579,"uid":34256,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"kyrie irving咁樣"},{"pid":"ab51a49d5eaa62f1c62dc0a96dd67f4f21d14534","tid":409579,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"Nigga"},{"pid":"37a2b2fe93a92726400113fea947ebde60af92f6","tid":409579,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:53:12.000Z","msg":"德國人已經癡左線"},{"pid":"87587ef012e67cec8e1e4da310e58a5395b3e849","tid":409579,"uid":86745,"like":169,"dislike":0,"score":169,"cited